Oily skin trying to make a comeback? not today😌

The @abib.global Airy sunstick keeps everything in check (and matte👀), thanks to oil-controlling powder + a waterproof formula that doesn’t melt away when life gets sweaty and greasy. Been there, done that😭

It goes on seamlessly with an airy soft blur, so no cakey mess, just smooth skin without whitecast. Plus the C-shape makes it way too easy to swipe and go, even on the run.

Now I want to know: are you team MATTE or GLOWY? Let me know in the comments💭

